go_data.justification: IL-1 had significant synergy with TSLP in cultures of CD4-CD8- thymocytes, indicating its role as a cytokine.
IL-1 synergized with TSLP to stimulate proliferation in cultures of CD4-CD8- thymocytes.
IL-1 is a cytokine that interacts with TSLP, which affects T lymphopoiesis, a process in the immune system.
